Terraform notes:-
============
***Terraform: Popular infrastucrure as a code
***Ansible: Configuration management or Configuration as a code
***Version control git: If you keep code in git you can maintain the history and you can get back previous versions.
***Consisten infrastucture: Same code will in all environment, So infrastucter is consistent in all environment.
***Automated infro--CRUD(Create, Read, Update, Delete)
***Cost optimisation: Create when required and stop or delete when not required.
***Automatic dependancy resource: we can create resource, Terraform will take care of dependancy managemnet .
